	encryption algorithm from aes-256-cbc to aes-256-gcm.

	* common.h (cmeGCMTagLen): Added define for the default AES-GCM
	authentication tag length (16 bytes).

	* crypto.c (cmeCipherInit): Added two-phase GCM initialization:
	first call sets cipher and IV length via EVP_CTRL_GCM_SET_IVLEN,
	second call supplies key and IV.

	* crypto.c (cmeCipherByteString): Added full AES-GCM support:
	detects GCM mode via EVP_CIPHER_mode(); on encryption appends the
	16-byte authentication tag after the ciphertext; on decryption
	strips and verifies the tag with EVP_CTRL_GCM_SET_TAG before
	accepting plaintext.  Non-GCM path (e.g. aes-256-cbc) is
	unchanged.

	* function_tests.c, function_tests.h
	(testCryptoSymmetricGCM_ByteString): Added encrypt/decrypt
	round-trip test for aes-256-gcm through cmeCipherByteString.

